body_html:
Do we need this change also in RC1?
@jbobba looks like not all the commits in the pull requests have the emails set up correctly, thus failing the CLA check.
The easiest way would be is to squash all of them and push them onto your branch.
Or you need to fix their author information individually.

Do we need this change also in RC1?
@jbobba looks like not all the commits in the pull requests have the emails set up correctly, thus failing the CLA check.
The easiest way would be is to squash all of them and push them onto your branch.
Or you need to fix their author information individually.
